TailnetKit

This software embeds and links Tailscale's tsnet library and depends on
tailscale.com and its transitive dependencies, distributed under the BSD
3-Clause License. Copyright (c) Tailscale Inc. & AUTHORS.

TailnetKit is an independent project. It is not affiliated with, endorsed by,
or sponsored by Tailscale Inc. The terms "Tailscale" and "tailnet" are used
only to describe interoperability with the Tailscale network.

Vendor/TailnetCore.xcframework is built from the Go sources in Go/ via gomobile
and statically includes compiled code from the dependencies pinned in
Go/go.mod and Go/go.sum. A full dependency and license inventory will accompany
binary releases.
